OL,3,CSix-year-old girls help catch
OL,4,Cshoplifter who tried to 'shush' them
OL,6,FA shoplifter who was caught by two six-
OL,7,Fyear-old girls despite trying to
OL,8,F'shush them' has been jailed.
OL,10,FPolice were called after reports that
OL,11,FAlan Morris, who was wanted for 22
OL,12,Fseparate offences in Blackpool in
OL,13,FOctober, was recognised.
OL,15,FThe 31-year-old led officers on a foot
OL,16,Fchase and believed he had escaped by
OL,17,Fhiding between a bin shed and a bush
OL,18,Fin a garden.
