OL,4,Cshoplifter who tried to 'shush' them
OL,6,FHowever, two girls saw Morris and
OL,7,Fpointed him out to the officers
OL,8,Fdespite the offender attempting to
OL,9,F'shush' them.
OL,11,FMorris, of no fixed address, was
OL,12,Farrest at the scene on Thursday, 7
OL,13,FNovember.
OL,15,FLancashire Constabulary said he has
OL,16,Fsince been given a nine-month prison
OL,17,Fsentence and a three year Criminal
OL,18,FBehaviour Order which bans him from
OL,19,Fentering any Asda and Tesco in
OL,20,FBlackpool.
