OL,3,CSix-year-old girls help catch
OL,4,Cshoplifter who tried to 'shush' them
OL,6,FThe girls who helped apprehend him
OL,7,Fwere visited by officers in their
OL,8,Fschool assembly, who awarded them a
OL,9,Fcertificate and chocolates.
OL,11,FSergeant Paul Regan said: "We wouldn't
OL,12,Fhave been able to detain the offender
OL,13,Fanywhere near as quick as we did if it
OL,14,Fwasn't for the help of these two
OL,15,Fgirls. They acted bravely and they
OL,16,Fshould be very proud of themselves."
